📦 File Uploads in Express with Multer
1. Why File Uploads Need Middleware

When a client uploads a file, it doesn’t send JSON. 
Instead, it sends data as multipart/form-data, which is:

A special format for sending files + text together
Sent as a stream of chunks, not a simple object
Not automatically parsed by Express

👉 That’s why middleware like Multer is needed:
To read and parse incoming file streams
To extract files and fields
To store files properly

